                      <item xml:id="a1">
                        <desc>
                          Hymn to <foreign xml:lang="gez">ደብረ፡ ሊባኖስ፡</foreign>, with incipit
                          <foreign xml:lang="gez">
                            ሰላም፡ ለኪ፡ ደብረ፡ ገነት፡ <lb/>
