                            ተገልበበት፡ ክብረ፡ ጸሎት፡ ሰማል፡ ለኪ፡...
                          </foreign>
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a2">
                        <desc type = "OwnershipNote"><locus target = "#174r"/>, col. 2, bottom: Note of ownership, name erased</desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a3">
                        <desc>
                          Scribal intervention: words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#5v #18v #33v #49r #70v"/>etc.);
                          and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target = "#14r #18r #20v #50r #150v"/>, etc.);
                          and in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted
                          (<locus target = "#11r"/>, line 3; <locus target = "#19r"/>, line 8; <locus target = "#27r"/>, line 12; <locus target = "#46v"/>, line 9; <locus target = "#48r"/>, line 12; <locus target = "#126r"/>, line 21; <locus target = "#137r"/>, line 17; <locus target = "#149r"/>, line 11; <locus target = "#149v"/>, line 13; <locus target = "#153v"/>, line 8),
                          and in another case where the symbol (+) is used (<locus target = "#21v"/>, line 4);
                          and in another case where the symbol (┴) is used for text written in the following line (<locus target = "#74r"/>, line 18);
                          and in another case in the bottom margin with the symbols ( and ┬) placed at either end of the line to mark the location (<locus target = "#27r"/>, line 19);
                          erasure markings are visible (<locus target = "#2r #12r #13r #14r #19v"/>, etc.); text has been removed (f. 112r)
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a6">
                        <desc>
                          The scribe’s chosen aspect ratio for the codex combined with the script size forces the scribe to complete the line of text
                          above or below the end of the line (throughout)
                        </desc>
                      </item>
                      <item xml:id="a7">
                        <desc>The codex has been paginated with a number (1–342) in the upper corner of each page</desc>
                      </item>

                      <item xml:id="e1">
                        <desc><locus target = "#132v #133r"/> is shot twice and given two numbers</desc>
                      </item>
